{
  "duration": 93.8,
  "language": "en",
  "text": "What industry did you decide to pursue a career? Movies which encompasses almost every industry. I'm here with Tom Cruise. It's nice to see you. You've been a top actor for decades. What's been the biggest driving factor of your success throughout your career? It is my desire to deliver the very best that I've always felt for myself. Even when I was a little kid before movies, when I had any job I always wanted to understand how to do that job and then do it at the very highest level that I possibly can. Where did you work at that come from? I enjoy going for that level of perfection and I surround myself with people that have that same care. My goal was always to make a movie and have it be the best possible film for an audience and then it makes some money so that studio could have that money and then go make other movies and I can go off and make other movies and that's my desire. I knew very early on that in a changing world the most important thing is one's own ability to change, to adapt, to learn. And your last message to the younger generation? You go. Well, I'm someone when I hear it can't be done. I'm like, I don't know, maybe, you know, how many times do you think that people aren't like, oh you could do this. So this is you hanging off a plane right? Oh yeah, it is. Do you not fear anything? No, it's not a matter. I don't mind being afraid. I want an adventurous life. I want it. And don't be so afraid to be afraid or nervous. The important thing is to keep pursuing your dreams and finding accurate things that are going to add to your life and to others. You know, the way that I look at life, I don't live it for myself. I know that to live my life, I'm thinking of others. And to lead is to serve. Not to tell people what to do, but to help them to be better. That's kind of what I do. You've got amazing advice. Thank you so much for your time. It's a pleasure, James. My pleasure.",
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 2.0,
      "text": "What industry did you decide to pursue a career?"
    },
    {
      "start": 2.2,
      "end": 5.1,
      "text": "Movies which encompasses almost every industry."
    },
    {
      "start": 5.3,
      "end": 6.1,
      "text": "I'm here with Tom Cruise."
    },
    {
      "start": 6.6,
      "end": 7.6,
      "text": "It's nice to see you."
    },
    {
      "start": 7.7,
      "end": 9.1,
