    },
    {
      "start": 9.5,
      "end": 12.2,
      "text": "What's been the biggest driving factor of your success throughout your career?"
    },
    {
      "start": 12.4,
      "end": 16.8,
      "text": "It is my desire to deliver the very best that I've always felt for myself."
